00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:04,800
Get some proper rest.

561
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:05,610
Got it.

562
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:09,720
I am more than ten years older than you.

563
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:11,800
Calling me "Auntie"
wouldn't be too much.

564
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:17,410
Bed 37's surgery has been
moved to the afternoon.

565
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:19,530
How did the last surgery go?

566
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:24,450
The patient had a sudden hemorrhage
during the procedure.

567
00:35:24,450 --> 00:35:25,480
Luckily, Director Li and I

568
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,760
found the bleeding spot in time.

569
00:35:27,130 --> 00:35:28,800
It went alright, pretty smooth overall.

570
00:35:32,130 --> 00:35:33,840
Where's Mingsheng? Has he gone back?

571
00:35:34,530 --> 00:35:35,320
Yeah, he left.

572
00:35:36,570 --> 00:35:38,800
I gave him everything
you asked me to pass on.

573
00:35:39,450 --> 00:35:42,720
He told me not to
let you know he came by.

574
00:35:44,930 --> 00:35:46,160
That little brat.

575
00:35:46,570 --> 00:35:47,530
Honestly,

576
00:35:47,530 --> 00:35:48,800
you and your son are the same.

577
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:50,760
You both say one thing and mean another.

578
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,720
You are both stubborn.

579
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:55,800
Like father, like son.

580
00:35:57,410 --> 00:35:59,050
Thanks for looking after Mingsheng

581
00:35:59,050 --> 00:36:01,530
these past few days.
I really appreciate it.

582
00:36:03,490 --> 00:36:04,320
Come on,

583
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:05,320
it was nothing.

584
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:07,970
I get to play the good guy.

585
00:36:11,450 --> 00:36:12,320
Here.

586
00:36:17,930 --> 00:36:18,720
By the way,

587
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,890
my parents are coming
to Huanzhou this weekend.

588
00:36:21,890 --> 00:36:23,490
Would you like to grab a meal with us?

589
00:36:27,570 --> 00:36:29,530
I get that you don't
want to go public with us.

590
00:36:29,530 --> 00:36:31,160
I already explained it to them.

591
00:36:31,160 --> 00:36:32,840
They will keep it between us.

592
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:34,610
It's just a casual dinner.

593
00:36:34,610 --> 00:36:35,360
No big deal.

594
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:35,800
Alright.

595
00:36:45,410 --> 00:36:46,200
Sure.

596
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,720
Let's have dinner.

597
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,720
Hurry up and eat. Take a nap after.

598
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:14,610
Qiao Qingyu.

599
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,530
Who are you?

600
00:37:20,610 --> 00:37:22,570
We got on great when we chatted online.

601
00:37:22,930 --> 00:37:24,200
You forgot me already?

602
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,320
You're Hei?

603
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:27,570
Yeah, that's me.

604
00:37:27,570 --> 00:37:28,930
Come on, let's talk.

605
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:31,160
I need to head home first.

606
00:37:31,160 --> 00:37:32,130
Hold on.

607
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,280
Weren't you the one

608
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,570
asking around about Hei?

609
00:37:35,570 --> 00:37:36,610
What's with the act?

610
00:37:37,160 --> 00:37:38,720
My mom is waiting for me at home.

611
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,610
You're going home this early?

612
00:37:41,610 --> 00:37:42,930
Where's the fun in that?

613
00:37:42,930 --> 00:37:45,160
Come on, let me treat you.

614
00:37:45,160 --> 00:37:47,360
Let's get something nice to eat, yeah?

615
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:50,610
There's a bubble tea shop
across the street that's popular.

616
00:37:50,610 --> 00:37:51,640
Let's go chat there.

617
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:53,970
Those guys don't look like good news.

618
00:37:55,010 --> 00:37:56,680
Can she really mess with those guys?

619
00:37:56,680 --> 00:37:57,680
Exactly. Let's go.

620
00:37:57,680 --> 00:37:59,450
It's almost rush hour.
Buses will be packed.

621
00:38:08,890 --> 00:38:10,360
You usually get your tea here?

622
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:12,720
This place looks pretty average.

623
00:38:14,410 --> 00:38:15,280
Listen up,

624
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:16,160
today everything's

625
00:38:16,160 --> 00:38:18,410
on Qiao Qingyu's big bro, Hei.

626
00:38:18,410 --> 00:38:19,610
Order whatever you like.

627
00:38:19,610 --> 00:38:20,680
Go on, it's on me.

628
00:38:20,680 --> 00:38:21,530
Move it.

629
00:38:23,530 --> 00:38:24,930
Order something. I'll pay.

630
00:38:25,610 --> 00:38:26,800
You know Qiao Qingyu, right?

631
00:38:27,490 --> 00:38:29,530
Come on. Sit.

632
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:39,450
Here you go.

633
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,320
Not bad.

634
00:38:47,720 --> 00:38:49,320
I'm a huge fan of milk tea too.

635
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,240
Go on, drink.

636
00:38:51,240 --> 00:38:52,130
We can order more.

637
00:38:54,610 --> 00:38:56,360
I'll just call you Baby from now on.

638
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:58,760
That's what I used to call your sister.

639
00:39:00,610 --> 00:39:02,680
How did you and Qiao Beiyu meet?

640
00:39:03,160 --> 00:39:04,840
I saved her. Like a hero.

641
00:39:07,010 --> 00:39:08,450
Outside a karaoke bar,

642
00:39:08,450 --> 00:39:09,970
some guy was harassing her.

643
00:39:09,970 --> 00:39:11,680
I stepped in and sorted it out.

644
00:39:12,530 --> 00:39:14,130
She was still
at the art school back then.

645
00:39:14,130 --> 00:39:15,720
She really loved singing.

646
00:39:16,490 --> 00:39:18,000
She hung out at my karaoke place a lot.

647
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,130
I always looked out for her.

648
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,640
And over time,

649
00:39:23,010 --> 00:39:24,450
we got together.

650
00:39:26,090 --> 00:39:27,320
Honestly,

651
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:29,640
your sister was seriously pretty.

652
00:39:29,640 --> 00:39:31,280
No way a girl like that
would fall for me.

653
00:39:32,130 --> 00:39:33,890
It felt like I'd struck gold.

654
00:39:33,890 --> 00:39:35,800
Of course I had to treat her right.

655
00:39:36,450 --> 00:39:39,360
For real,
I slowly fell in love with her.

656
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:40,680
Whatever she said, I'd go with it.

657
00:39:42,410 --> 00:39:44,450
But after a while,
it just didn't feel the same.

658
00:39:45,160 --> 00:39:46,800
She wasn't anything special.

659
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:49,050
Your sister was just naive.

660
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:52,450
Any guy could sweet-talk her
and she'd fall for it.

661
00:39:52,450 --> 00:39:54,890
Literally, any guy would do.

662
00:39:56,970 --> 00:39:58,410
Hey, come a bit closer.

663
00:39:59,610 --> 00:40:01,010
I didn't mean to scare you.

664
00:40:01,010 --> 00:40:02,410
I just get pissed off

665
00:40:03,720 --> 00:40:04,800
whenever I think about her.

666
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,320
But I can tell

667
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:08,890
you're not like her.

668
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,160
You are

669
00:40:13,610 --> 00:40:15,010
the innocent type.

670
00:40:15,010 --> 00:40:16,240
Do you have a boyfriend?

671
00:40:16,240 --> 00:40:18,010
So you met in Huanzhou?

672
00:40:18,610 --> 00:40:19,450
Yeah.

673
00:40:19,600 --> 00:40:20,610
Then, I got the wrong guy.

674
00:40:20,610 --> 00:40:21,360
What do you mean?

675
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,610
Sit down, I'll explain.

676
00:40:22,970 --> 00:40:24,610
No, I'm the right one.

677
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,410
We're meant to meet.

678
00:40:26,410 --> 00:40:27,530
You were looking for me.

679
00:40:28,130 --> 00:40:29,680
You know, I saw you years ago.

680
00:40:29,680 --> 00:40:31,200
When did you ever see me?

681
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,010
You don't remember?

682
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:35,280
Outside the art school. Think about it.

683
00:40:49,640 --> 00:40:52,320
Baby! Baby!

684
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:54,680
I've been waiting forever.
Come on, give me a hug.

685
00:40:56,970 --> 00:40:59,130
I bought you flowers. Do you like them?

686
00:41:01,050 --> 00:41:01,930
Thanks.

687
00:41:01,930 --> 00:41:03,570
Come on, don't act like a stranger.

688
00:41:03,970 --> 00:41:05,360
You've been in class all day.

689
00:41:05,930 --> 00:41:06,640
Aren't you tired?

690
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:07,450
I'm okay.

691
00:41:08,160 --> 00:41:09,570
I'm kinda hungry. Let's grab dinner.

692
00:41:09,570 --> 00:41:11,720
Come on.
I've already booked a seafood spot.

693
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:12,840
Let's go. I'll drive.

694
00:41:13,890 --> 00:41:16,280
Qiao Beiyu!

695
00:41:19,680 --> 00:41:21,530
I came to Huanzhou
for the Mathematical Olympiad.

696
00:41:21,530 --> 00:41:24,280
Mom asked me to bring you some fruit.

697
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:25,840
Who are you?

698
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:28,050
I don't know you.

699
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,800
You're her sister from her hometown?

700
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:32,570
I just said I don't know her.

701
00:41:32,570 --> 00:41:33,720
Go. Let's go.

702
00:41:34,050 --> 00:41:34,680
I'm starving.

703
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:36,050
The kid really looks like you.

704
00:41:36,050 --> 00:41:37,280
I told you, I don't know her.

705
00:41:41,970 --> 00:41:42,760
Baby.

706
00:41:43,010 --> 00:41:43,450
Qiao Beiyu!

707
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,890
I don't know you either!
Not now, not ever.

708
00:41:47,680 --> 00:41:50,490
But you're the one
I care about most. I mean it.

709
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,130
Hurry up and drive.

710
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:02,160
Actually, I knew what your sister
was thinking back then.

711
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:03,720
She did it for you.

712
00:42:03,720 --> 00:42:04,530
She cared about you.

713
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:06,570
Even though you were still young,

714
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:10,530
she didn't want you
to get mixed up with someone like me.

715
00:42:10,530 --> 00:42:11,530
But it didn't work.

716
00:42:11,970 --> 00:42:14,530
We know each other now,
and it's not too late.

717
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:18,890
Also, just look at you.

718
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:21,240
You've really grown into a beauty.

719
00:42:21,930 --> 00:42:22,970
Even prettier than before.

720
00:42:22,970 --> 00:42:23,640
Don't touch me.

721
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:24,800
What if I do?

722
00:42:24,800 --> 00:42:26,200
Stay away from me. Don't...

723
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:27,200
Don't touch me!

724
00:42:27,200 --> 00:42:28,200
Hey, what are you doing?

725
00:42:28,200 --> 00:42:29,200
From now on, you're mine.

726
00:42:29,200 --> 00:42:30,800
Your sister owed me. You'll pay it back.

727
00:43:02,381 --> 00:43:04,601
♪Maybe♪

728
00:43:06,461 --> 00:43:11,861
♪The more I care,
the more I tread carefully♪

729
00:43:13,551 --> 00:43:18,901
♪Counting the distance between us♪

730
00:43:19,801 --> 00:43:26,061
♪Just one step away from reaching♪

731
00:43:31,061 --> 00:43:33,351
♪The future♪

732
00:43:35,051 --> 00:43:40,671
♪Time will unveil this mystery♪

733
00:43:42,251 --> 00:43:47,611
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

734
00:43:48,461 --> 00:43:54,771
♪But one that never expires♪

735
00:43:57,091 --> 00:44:02,141
♪Turns out, all my thoughts♪

736
00:44:02,241 --> 00:44:06,551
♪Spell your name♪

737
00:44:06,841 --> 00:44:12,851
♪The one and only stubbornness
in my heart♪

738
00:44:13,071 --> 00:44:16,381
♪From the very first glance♪

739
00:44:16,731 --> 00:44:20,801
♪I started painting
what our future would look like♪

740
00:44:20,801 --> 00:44:27,071
♪That's when the dream began
to feel real♪

741
00:44:27,071 --> 00:44:30,731
♪Turns out♪

742
00:44:31,051 --> 00:44:35,111
♪Your heart had a place for me too♪

743
00:44:35,511 --> 00:44:41,491
♪Cradling the same story we both knew♪

744
00:44:41,761 --> 00:44:45,421
♪Thankfully, we were naïve enough♪

745
00:44:45,421 --> 00:44:48,961
♪And brave just in time♪

746
00:44:48,961 --> 00:44:55,941
♪To make sure our moments
weren't lost to time♪
